{
  "$description": "Draftr semantic tokens — import as a Figma Variable collection named 'Semantic'. Create two modes: 'Light' and 'Dark'. Every $value aliases a primitive from the 'Primitives' collection using {path.to.primitive} syntax. Zero hardcoded values.",
